            <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;별점--&#34;&gt;별점 : ★★☆☆☆&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3174.414552767098!2d127.0127544!3d37.2853077!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x357b43bf43f4bedd%3A0x4bafa109f6109b41!2z7ZaJ66as64uo6ri4!5e0!3m2!1sko!2skr!4v1774998936924!5m2!1sko!2skr&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; style=&#34;border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;no-referrer-when-downgrade&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;한똥이랑 만났다. 갈 곳도 하고싶은 것도 없어서 멍한 나를 위해 데려간 곳.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34; height=&#34;6048&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/1.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/1_hu_8ec10441dee9ed71.jpg 800w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/1_hu_22f13c9ea79ff6aa.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/1_hu_54a65babea1893b5.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/1.jpg 8064w&#34; width=&#34;8064&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;여러 공방도 있고, 볼거리가 있다고 들었다고 해서 갔는데&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;공방 몇개가 있긴 했지만 닫혀있었고, 4컷사진 찍는 곳과 음식점 뿐. 아, 아기자기한 소품 파는 곳도 있었다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34; height=&#34;6048&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/2.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/2_hu_52d0e1022bdee734.jpg 800w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/2_hu_e95ceac6f7ecb0d4.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/2_hu_f6dcaa04fccc7c6d.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/2.jpg 8064w&#34; width=&#34;8064&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;인도와 차도를 구분하기 위해 만들어 놓은 듯한 파이프. 안에 꽃을 심어놓았더니 엄청 이뻤다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34; height=&#34;6048&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/3.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/3_hu_2eb1a97aa870e996.jpg 800w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/3_hu_ff80c977b9037da8.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/3_hu_8d1e035f59625701.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/3.jpg 8064w&#34; width=&#34;8064&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;180px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;75&#34; height=&#34;8064&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/4.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/4_hu_8c08362c8fbc23a.jpg 800w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/4_hu_c6f44098b278935.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/4_hu_ca3d84338ca3ade7.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/4.jpg 6048w&#34; width=&#34;6048&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34; height=&#34;3024&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/5.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/5_hu_d57c5b64a9d6b76f.jpg 800w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/5_hu_388dc03ed950b141.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/5_hu_204df3873ed51618.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/5.jpg 4032w&#34; width=&#34;4032&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;골목 골목 다니다보니, 좁은 골목에 이렇게 인형? 오브제를 담장에 놔둔 곳도 찾을 수 있었다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;사진 찍기 좋은데?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34; height=&#34;6048&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/6.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/6_hu_4171f37730f735d0.jpg 800w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/6_hu_49e3a65d1521710c.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/6_hu_12c74c145c7e8b10.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:1313/reviewlog/post/26040103/6.jpg 8064w&#34; width=&#34;8064&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;한똥이 바이크 사고싶다고 해서, 절대 안된다고 말렸다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;근데 이쁘긴 하더라. 카페 앞 바이크.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;볼 거 별로 없음.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;주차장은 좁았고, 커플들은 많았다. 볼 건 없었다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;나중에 만일 여자친구가 생긴다 하더라도 여기는 데려오고 싶지 않은 곳.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
